window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>It was a quiet Seattle morning until the skies filled with fire: without warning, a catastrophic meteor shower caused buildings to crumble and the lights to go out. Out of the rubble, five ordinary people arose to find themselves manifesting undreamed-of abilities. </p> <p>Will they be enough to do what the military cannot - stop a massive alien invasion before the entire West Coast is destroyed? </p>"; 
